        "text": [
          " لَا يَرْتَمِسُ الْمُحْرِمُ فِي الْمَاءِ ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.hubeali": [
            "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Hammad Bin Isa, from Hareyz, from the one who informed him, ",
            "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The one in <span class=\"iTxt\">Ihraam</span> cannot immerse himself into the water’."
          ],
          "en.sarwar": [
            "1. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from Hammad ibn ‘Isa from Hariz from those whom narrated to him who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘One in the state of Ihram must not submerge his head in the water.”’ "
          ]
        }
